                        <h3 class="post-title">
                            <a href="http://voxday.blogspot.co.uk/2018/03/infogalactic-update.html">Infogalactic update</a>
                        </h3>
                    

                    <div class="post-body">
                        <div>
                            <div style="clear:both;"></div>We made some major changes to the Infogalactic structure yesterday. While most of the work is interior stuff that will not be readily apparent to the user, we have significantly expanded our storage and processing capabilities while reducing our monthly burn rate by about one-third. This means that we are running about twice as fast and about 2.7 times more efficiently than before, while giving us considerably more control over our backend.<br />
<br />
