                    <div class="post-body">
                        <div>
                            <div style="clear:both;"></div>It's called "immigration-based identity politics" and it's merely <a href="https://www.bozemandailychronicle.com/ap_news/politics/democratic-republican-voter-bases-are-more-different-than-ever-study/article_6c34e7a9-f6a1-539f-96ea-1ad11a64d6b5.html">a matter of scale</a>:<br />
