                            <div style="clear:both;"></div>I'm still trying to figure out how self-driving cars can possibly be economically viable, <a href="http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5519433/Self-driving-Uber-car-runs-kills-pedestrian-Arizona.html">considering the ruinous insurance costs</a> that will be involved:<br />
